t3.title: Branch Filtering Name Augmentation Test 01
t3.desc:
Tests setting of effective key scope and resource names using branch filtering when
    there are nested scopes and topicrefs.

t4.title: Keyscope Test 01 Description
t4.desc:
Verifies that keys defined on topicrefs that also specify @keyscope are
    in the specified scope and not the parent scope.

t6.title: This-Topic Fragment ID Test 01
t6.desc:
Tests the resolution of this-topic fragment IDs within elements used by content
    reference.
